557
00:54:35,225 --> 00:54:36,851
Maafkan ibu, Anakku.

558
00:54:41,189 --> 00:54:42,690
Maaf untuk apa?

559
00:54:43,191 --> 00:54:45,068
Kenapa meminta maaf?

560
00:54:49,489 --> 00:54:52,033
Dahulu hanya teriris pisau sedikit saja

561
00:54:52,325 --> 00:54:54,536
