630
00:59:34,107 --> 00:59:36,234
Itu saja cukup bagiku.

631
01:01:01,402 --> 01:01:02,570
Seo-woo.

632
01:01:11,621 --> 01:01:12,997
Bibi cantik itu

633
01:01:14,415 --> 01:01:15,291
adalah

634
01:01:18,836 --> 01:01:20,087
ibu

635
01:01:23,257 --> 01:01:24,342
