- Apa ini?
- Daging babi.

704
01:06:11,921 --> 01:06:12,880
- Enak.
- Benar?

705
01:06:12,963 --> 01:06:15,174
Seo-woo, Nenek lelah.

706
01:06:15,257 --> 01:06:16,175
Seo-woo.

